programDescription: The PMP certification provides a thorough understanding of project management principles, processes, and methodologies.
It equips professionals with the skills to lead and direct projects effectively, ensuring successful outcomes and stakeholder satisfaction.
Upholding ethical standards and professional conduct is integral to maintaining the credibility and integrity of the PMP certification.
